additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Ingredients: Dairy ingredients (reconstituted skim milk and/or reconstituted buttermilk, butter oil, cream), sugar, cocoa components (11%^)(cocoa mass, cocoa butter), glucose, vegetable oil, emulsifiers (E471, soy lecithin, sunflower lecithin), stabilisers (E410, E412, E407, E401), flavour, colour (E141), pea protein, salt, maltodextrin, erythritol, sucralose. Contains milk, soy. May contain wheat, gluten, peanut, tree nuts.
